\title{Questions about taxiing procedures}
\maketitle

\section{Ground controllers}	
\begin{itemize}
    \item Which informations are available to the ground controllers? Examples: scheduled time of take-off, available parking slots?
\end{itemize}

\section{Pilots}
\begin{itemize}
    \item How autonomous are pilots during the taxiing?
    \item Which informations do they have? Examples : path to follow, number of taxiing planes ... 
   
\end{itemize}
